םיבקנ םיבקנ / all the openings. We regularly perceive by contrast: light and
shadow, height and depth, loudness and softness...Often we become aware
of health only after illness has replaced it. This brief paragraph of praise
for the wondrous workings of the human organism encourages recognition
of the blessing of health in its presence, not its absence. Every moment
we are healing!    /SC/XXE.G./XX/PR

